data.title: Brian Wilson Extends Pet Sounds Tour
data.meta_description: More North American shows celebrating the 50th anniversary of the album
data.text:
Brian Wilson has extended his tour in celebration of the 50th anniversary of Pet Sounds. The new North American leg of Pet Sounds: The Final Performances will begin March 27, 2017 in Orlando and take him throughout the United States. The tour was initially announced this past January, and included a stop at Pitchfork Music Festival in Chicago. Find the remainder of his 2016 shows and full list of 2017 dates below.

It was revealed earlier this month that Wilson was working on a new album of “rock 'n' roll classics” and possibly new material. His new autobiography, I Am Brian Wilson: A Memoir, is out today. Read the introduction and first chapter from the book here.
